---
title: Southeast Asian Salt & Pepper Chicken with Rice, Honey-Soy Veggies & Sesame Dressing
description: You've had salt and pepper squid, but have you tried salt and pepper chicken? The secret to this delicious meal is coating the
chicken with our Southeast Asian spice blend - it makes every crunchy bite a taste sensation!
